news.message: Add Sevagoth Prime to your Arsenal today!

translations.en: Add Sevagoth Prime to your Arsenal today!
translations.fr: Ajoutez Sevagoth Prime à votre Arsenal dès aujourd'hui !
translations.it: Aggiungi Sevagoth Prime al tuo Arsenale oggi!
translations.de: Fügt Sevagoth Prime noch heute eurem Arsenal hinzu!
translations.es: ¡Agrega a Sevagoth Prime a tu arsenal hoy mismo!
translations.pt: Adicione o Sevagoth Prime ao seu Arsenal hoje mesmo!
translations.ru: Добавьте Севагота Прайм в свой арсенал уже сегодня!
translations.pl: Dodajcie Sevagotha Prime do swojego Arsenału już dziś!
translations.uk: Додайте Севаґота-прайм до своєї зброярні вже сьогодні!
translations.ja: Sevagoth Primeを今すぐアーセナルに加えよう！
translations.zh: 今天就将 Sevagoth Prime 添加到你的军械库！
translations.ko: 세바고스 프라임을 지금 여러분의 무기고에 추가해 보세요!
translations.tc: 今天就把 Sevagoth Access 添加至你的軍械庫中！

news.asString: [54d 22h 12m 0s ago] [Add Sevagoth Prime to your Arsenal today!](https://www.warframe.com/prime-access?utm_medium=in-game&utm_source=in-game&utm_campaign=2024-08-SevagothPrimeLaunch)

news.message: Nova Prime and Trinity Prime return!

translations.en: Nova Prime and Trinity Prime return!
translations.fr: Nova Prime et Trinity Prime sont de retour !
translations.it: Tornano Nova Prime e Trinity Prime!
translations.de: Nova Prime und Trinity Prime kehren zurück!
translations.es: ¡Nova Prime y Trinity Prime están de regreso!
translations.pt: A Nova Prime e a Trinity Prime retornaram!
translations.ru: Нова Прайм и Тринити Прайм возвращаются!
translations.pl: Nova Prime i Trinity Prime powracają!
translations.tr: Nova Prime ve Trinity Prime geri dönüyor!
translations.zh: Nova Prime 和 Trinity Prime 回归！
translations.tc: Nova Prime 以及 Trinity Prime 回歸！

news.message: Earn a FREE Caliban Warframe Oct 2-16

translations.en: Earn a FREE Caliban Warframe Oct 2-16
translations.fr: Gagnez une Warframe Caliban GRATUITE du 2 au 16 octobre
translations.it: Ottieni un Warframe Caliban GRATUITO dal 2 al 16 Ottobre
translations.de: Verdient euch vom 2. bis 16. Oktober einen KOSTENLOSEN Caliban-Warframe
translations.es: Gana un warframe Caliban GRATIS del 2 al 16 de octubre
translations.pt: Obtenha um Warframe Caliban gratuito entre os dias 2 e 16 de outubro
translations.ru: Получите БЕСПЛАТНЫЙ варфрейм Калибан со 2 по 16 октября
translations.pl: Zdobądźcie darmowego Warframe'a Calibana między 2 a 16 października
translations.tr: 3-17 Ekim tarihleri arasında ÜCRETSİZ bir Caliban Warframe kazanın
translations.ja: 10月3日から17日までCalibanを無料でゲット
translations.zh: 在美东夏令时间 10 月 2 日至 16 日免费领取 Caliban 战甲
translations.ko: 북미 시각 10월 2일-16일 동안 칼리반 워프레임을 무료로 획득하세요
translations.tc: 在 10 月 2 日至 16 日免費獲得一個 Caliban Warframe

news.asString: [12d 22h 2m 0s ago] [Earn a FREE Caliban Warframe Oct 2-16](https://www.warframe.com/news/calibans-new-adaptations?utm_medium=in-game&utm_source=in-game&utm_campaign=2024-09-CalibanGiveaway)
